---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageSeo from '../components/seo/PageSeo.astro';
import LegalPageShell from '../components/legal/LegalPageShell.astro';
import { standalonePages } from '../../site-pages';

const page = standalonePages.privacyPolicy;
---

<BaseLayout>
  <PageSeo slot="head" title={page.title} description={page.description} />

  <LegalPageShell
    eyebrow="Personal Data"
    title="Privacy Policy"
    updated="June 10, 2026"
  >
    <section class="legal-section">
      <h2>Data controller</h2>
      <div class="legal-copy">
        <p>
          The data controller is Isaure Lohest d'Hooghvorst, reachable at
          <a href="mailto:isaure.lohest@gmail.com">isaure.lohest@gmail.com</a>.
        </p>
        <p>
          Isaure Lohest d'Hooghvorst operates through JobYourself Coop, VAT number
          BE 0479 233 349, Chaussée de Charleroi 112, 1060 Brussels, Belgium.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-section">
      <h2>Data collected</h2>
      <div class="legal-copy">
        <p>
          When you use the contact form, the site collects the information you provide:
          name, email address, and message content.
        </p>
        <p>
          Technical information may also be processed automatically, such as the page or
          domain of origin of the request, the date sent, the IP address, or technical logs
          required for the security and proper functioning of the site.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-section">
      <h2>Purposes</h2>
      <div class="legal-copy">
        <p>The data is used to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>respond to your contact or project request;</li>
          <li>prepare a discussion, estimate, or collaboration proposal;</li>
          <li>ensure the security, maintenance, and technical operation of the site;</li>
          <li>measure site traffic when analytics tools are active.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-section">
      <h2>Legal bases</h2>
      <div class="legal-copy">
        <p>
          Processing related to the contact form is based on the performance of
          pre-contractual measures when your request concerns a project, or on the legitimate
          interest of Isaure Lohest d'Hooghvorst in responding to messages received.
        </p>
        <p>
          Processing strictly necessary for the operation and security of the site is based on
          legitimate interest. Non-essential trackers, in particular certain audience
          measurement tools, may require your prior consent depending on their configuration.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-section">
      <h2>Recipients</h2>
      <div class="legal-copy">
        <p>
          The data is intended for Isaure Lohest d'Hooghvorst and, where necessary, technical
          providers involved in hosting, email delivery, security, or maintenance of the site.
        </p>
        <p>No personal data is sold to third parties.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-section">
      <h2>Retention</h2>
      <div class="legal-copy">
        <p>
          Requests sent via the form are kept for as long as necessary to process your
          message, then for up to three years after the last exchange if no project is
          undertaken.
        </p>
        <p>
          When a collaboration begins, certain data may be kept for longer in order to comply
          with applicable accounting, tax, or contractual obligations.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-section">
      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <div class="legal-copy">
        <p>
          This site uses Google Analytics to understand page traffic and improve the
          experience. This tool may place or read trackers on your device.
        </p>
        <p>
          You can limit or delete cookies from your browser settings. If a consent module is
          displayed on the site, you can also change your choices there.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-section">
      <h2>Your rights</h2>
      <div class="legal-copy">
        <p>
          You may request access, rectification, erasure, restriction, or portability of your
          data, and object to certain processing where permitted by law.
        </p>
        <p>
          To exercise your rights, contact
          <a href="mailto:isaure.lohest@gmail.com">isaure.lohest@gmail.com</a>. If you believe
          your rights are not being respected, you can file a complaint with the Belgian Data
          Protection Authority:
          <a href="https://www.autoriteprotectiondonnees.be/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"
            >autoriteprotectiondonnees.be</a
          >.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-section">
      <h2>Security</h2>
      <div class="legal-copy">
        <p>
          Isaure Lohest d'Hooghvorst implements reasonable measures to protect data
          transmitted via the site against unauthorized access, loss, alteration, or
          disclosure.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </LegalPageShell>
</BaseLayout>
